overview: “A zany spoof all about a boy who finds out too late that his entire teenage years were just spent in a wasted fantasy – a crazy fantasy called Fanny! Cute, blonde, and oh so adorably sexy. But she's just a comic character – or is she?”
tagline: It's wild & loony, new & groovy! A zany x-rated soap opera.
title: The Boob Tube Strikes Again!
